%h2.sub-title
  Contact information
- form_for @user, :url => {:action => "update_contact_information"}, :html => {:class => 'generic-form'} do |f|
  = f.error_messages(:header_message => nil, :class => "error")
  = render :partial => 'edit_contact_information_form', :object => f
  = f.submit "Next", :class => 'form-submit-button next-button'
